d":"2849cf313cf490d7a62f499baa407213adb854b9","tid":1437962,"uid":60740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:19:11.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:06:23.000Z","msg":"和班非一定要有哩個新裝備！一齊減少手足落單！應對防暴突襲！<br />\n<br />\n見到班防暴做埋畜蟲既野，就諗起自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425253</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}